Don’t spend 3 hours trying to fix one thing unless you know what you’re doing. If you get stuck on something, move on. You can always comment something out and come back to it. When I say comment it out, I don’t mean:

//blahblah
//blah
//b
//b

I mean:

/*blahblah
blah
b
b*/
